\usepackage{titletoc}
\usepackage{lipsum}

\begin{document}
\tableofcontents

\section{Introduction}
\lipsum[1]

\section{Methodology}
\lipsum[2]

\section{Results}
\lipsum[3]

\section{Conclusion}
\lipsum[4]

\end{document}
```

**Output:**

```
Table of Contents

1. Introduction
2. Methodology
3. Results
4. Conclusion
```

